quran[9{c,v,t}:
41,21,"woh apne jism ki khaalon se kahin ge"" tum ne hamaray khilaaf kyun gawahi di ?"" woh jawab den gi"" hamein usi khuda ne goyai di hai jis ne har cheez ko goya kar diya hai usi ne tum ko pehli martaba peda kya tha aur ab usi ki taraf tum wapas laaye ja rahay ho"
41,22,tum duniya mein juraim karte waqt jab chaptay thay to tumhe yeh khayaal nah tha ke kabhi tumahray apne kaan aur tumhari ankhen aur tumahray jism ki khalin tum par gawahi den gi balkay tum ne to yeh samgha tha ke tumahray bohat se aamaal ki Allah ko bhi khabar nahi hai
41,23,"tumhara yahi gumaan jo tum ne apne rab ke sath kya tha, tumhe le dooba aur isi ki badolat tum khasaray mein par gay """
41,24,"is haalat mein woh sabr karen ( ya nah karen ) aag hi un ka thikana ho gi, aur agar rujoo ka mauqa chahain ge to koi mauqa inhen nah diya jaye ga"
41,25,"hum ne un par aisay saathi musallat kar diye thay jo inhen agay aur peechay har cheez khushnuma bana kar dikhata thay, aakhir-kaar unn par bhi wohi faisla azaab chaspan ho kar raha jo un se pehlay guzray hue junoo aur insanon ke garohoon par chaspan ho chuka tha, yaqeenan woh khasaray mein reh jaane walay thay"
41,26,"yeh munkareen haq kehte hain"" iss quran ko hargiz nah suno aur jab yeh sunaya jaye to is mein khlal daalo, shayad ke is terhan tum ghalib aa jao """
41,27,inn kafiroon ko hum sakht azaab ka maza chakkha kar rahen ge aur jo bad tareen harkaat yeh karte rahay hain un ka poora poora badla aِnhin den ge
41,28,woh dozakh hai jo Allah ke dushmanon ko badlay mein miley gi usi mein hamesha hamesha ke liye inn ka ghar ho ga yeh hai saza iss jurm ki ke woh hamari ayaat ka inkaar karte rahay
41,29,"wahan yeh kafir kahin ge ke"" ae hamaray rab, zara hamein dikha day unn junoo aur insanon ko jinhon ne hamein gumraah kya tha, hum inhen paon taley roond dalain ge taakay woh khoob zaleel o khawar hon """
